      <title>关税影响下美国木材行业将终结加拿大的主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/us-lumber-industry-set-to-end-canada-s-dominance-as-tariffs-take-toll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于数十年的贸易限制造成影响，美国南部地区即将超越加拿大在北美木材行业的长期主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/us-lumber-industry-set-to-end-canada-s-dominance-as-tariffs-take-toll</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 18:12:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
